  to come together and share an exciting and engaging play experience! (Mus
 t be 18 months-younger 3 years old with an adult\, adult involvement is re
 quired)Adults attending with their child(ren) do NOT need to register. Ple
 ase add any additional registrants to your registration if more than one c
 hild that will be participating in the program.Registration will open at 9
 :00AM on Wednesday\, March 4th for Manheim Township and East Lampeter resi
 dents and on Friday\, March 6th for residents of other municipalities.Stor
 ytime PoliciesProgram Limits - Patrons are limited to one session of multi
 ple session programs per week.No Show – Patrons failing to cancel their 
 registration for more than 2 library programs in a month will be restricte
 d from registering for future programs for a period of one month’s time.
  Please cancel your registrations at least 2 hours prior to the start of t
 he program to allow for those on the waiting list to be notified of their 
 change in registration status.Late Arrivals – Please arrive 10 minutes p
 rior to the start of the program to allow for parking and other circumstan
 ces. The program will begin promptly at the designated time. At this time\
 , your spot will be forfeited to those on the wait list who will be grante
 d entry. If spots remain\, registrants may be allowed into the program. Ho
 wever\, registrants will not be permitted to enter the program 5 minutes p
 ast the start time.Accompanying Adults – This program is for adults and 
 children to enjoy together. Please plan to attend and be engaged with your
  child. Drop offs will not be permitted.Cancellations- Please check your e
 mail prior to departing to verify that the program has not been cancelled.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Lapp Story Silo
