 ompany. Where will your taste buds take us?🍽️Cooks & Books is an oppo
 rtunity for passionate home cooks to gather around the table for conversat
 ion over a potluck feast of delicious food made from the recipes of a feat
 ured chef\, food blog\, or cookbook. Why not invite a friend to join you? 
