 ading\, Babies\, Toddlers\, Children\n\nWelcome to Family Story Time at th
 e Manheim Community Library!You will find us in the Breakout Room of the K
 reider Farms Cultural Center. Please join us for stories\, crafts\, and ac
 tivities!This program contains crafts that may be difficult for babies/tod
 dlers\, but we encourage you to try it! They may surprise you. We attempt 
 new motor skills often and encourage parents to help or step back as much 
 as they are comfortable.Family Story Time is an independent registration t
 ype. Please register for every day you plan to attend. All (and only) chil
 dren should be registered. This gives me an idea of how many chairs/tables
 \, as well as supplies. Drop-offs will not be permitted\, and registration
  is required. If you realize you can't make it to Story Time\, please info
 rm Esther Martin by emailing her at emartin@manheimlibrary.org. You can al
 so call the front desk at (717)665-6700 Ext. 4200. Please let us know as s
 oon as you can because we often have a waitlist\, and we want everyone to 
 get the chance to participate if possible.
LOCATION:Manheim Community\, MAN Break-out Room
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/family-story-time-winter
 -series-154262
