 ernet safely and protecting your information?Unbox Your New Tech - NEW Cla
 ss!Consider stopping in at the Columbia Public Library for FREE one-on-one
  assistance. Doran is available every Tuesday\, Wednesday\, and Thursday 1
 0:00am - 3:00pm to assist you.Phillip is available Monday\, Wednesday\, an
 d Friday 10:00am - 1:00pm to assist you. Bring your own laptop or use one 
 of ours at the library. Appointments are recommended but not required. If 
 you'd like to set up an appointment with Doran\, please email: doran.condo
 n@millersville.edu or call 717-871-5951.
