SUMMARY:Wind\, Weather and Water
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260408T163000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260408T173000
UID:d854e85fc9d41654a9b84e92acf591ef@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:STEM\, Children\n\nGet ready to experiment! Young scientists w
 ill explore how wind and water work together to create weather. Kids will 
