UID:c12d9a508366acb4ef30012c1fc747e2@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Community\, Health & Wellness\, Children\, Tweens\, Teens\, Ad
 ults\n\nLancaster County Chooses Love is partnering with the Lancaster Pub
 lic Library to provide a safe and supportive space for LGBTQIA+ individual
 s and their families during drop-in office hours. During these informal of
 fice hours\, an advisor from Lancaster County Chooses Love will be availab
 le in one of our private study rooms for patrons to ask questions and lear
 n about LGBTQIA+ issues and experiences.   PLEASE NOTE: These office hours
  are a learning opportunity and are NOT a substitute for counseling. Litit
 z Chooses Love advisors are not trained mental health professionals and ca
 nnot offer professional counseling.All ages* · No registration is require
 d · Walk-ins welcome *Per Lancaster Public Library policy\, ages 11 and y
 ounger must be accompanied\, at all times\, by a caregiver who is 14 or ol
